Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.05,0:00:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want to do today?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.51,0:00:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.77,0:00:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Playing house got a little boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.77,0:00:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.81,0:00:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder when Mommy's visitors\Nare going to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.69,0:00:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,They should go home already.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.86,0:00:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.87,0:00:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.88,0:00:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw a doll walking down the path.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.34,0:00:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,A really big doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.72,0:01:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,She seemed like bad news for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.44,0:01:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Mommy, Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.73,0:01:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Ann!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.19,0:01:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,-I see what you're saying, but...\N-It's important to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.24,0:01:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yes, but...\N-Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.16,0:01:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Ann! Don't I always tell you\Nthat you have to knock first?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.37,0:01:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, a proper greeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.21,0:01:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to our home.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.71,0:01:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,-Pardon me, Mother.\N-My.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.42,0:01:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.68,0:01:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.18,0:01:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you find another strange bug?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.27,0:01:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,-I don't want to see it though, okay?\N-It's not a bug!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.98,0:01:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw a doll walking over!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.86,0:01:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,A doll?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.44,0:01:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Madam.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.19,0:01:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,She's arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.61,0:02:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that Doll! That was today, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.33,0:02:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Please show her in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.66,0:02:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yes, madam.\N-Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.75,0:02:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very sorry, but we'll have to\Ndo this another time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.04,0:02:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, what are you going to do\Nwith this mansion?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.71,0:02:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,She can't live here on her own.\NThat's why we offered--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.46,0:02:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Please come back another time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.38,0:02:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.23,0:02:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ann.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.19,0:02:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Be a good girl, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.07,0:02:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.28,0:02:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming all this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.95,0:02:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.20,0:02:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,She talks!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.33,0:02:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I will travel anywhere\Nto meet your request.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.58,0:02:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Auto Memory Doll--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.04,0:02:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew you were a doll!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.88,0:02:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ann!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.67,0:02:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-I'm sorry.\N-No apology necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.97,0:03:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet Evergarden at your service.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.01,0:03:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, have a seat.\NWould you like some tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.23,0:03:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope it's to your liking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.57,0:03:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,-Please help yourself.\N-Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.03,0:03:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,She's drinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.45,0:03:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,-What happens to the tea you drink?\N-Ann.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.37,0:03:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It will eventually be expelled from\Nmy body and return to earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.21,0:03:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Ann, you're being rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.04,0:03:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we begin?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.09,0:03:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand that I have been hired\Nfor a seven-day period.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.26,0:03:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'd like to get started right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.14,0:03:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.55,0:03:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Where shall we work?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.81,0:03:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, how about we do it in the sunroom\Nwhere it's bright?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.02,0:03:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,-What are you going to do?\N-She's helping me write a letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.02,0:03:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I can write a letter for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.73,0:04:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know how to spell\Nthe hard words yet, Ann.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.82,0:04:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.70,0:04:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, Ms. Violet is very famous\Nfor being a very good letter writer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.29,0:04:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is the letter to?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.46,0:04:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.79,0:04:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone very far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.17,0:04:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,-Far away?\N-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.59,0:04:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an important letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.80,0:04:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not allowed in the sunroom, okay?\NShall we, Miss Violet?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.39,0:04:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.89,0:04:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the typewriter I brought.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.36,0:04:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That is fine with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.23,0:04:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.28,0:04:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew she was bad news.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.20,0:04:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,She really is a doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.17,0:04:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Madam!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.97,0:05:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Mommy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.05,0:05:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.06,0:05:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get better in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.60,0:05:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.56,0:05:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.77,0:05:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I know! I'll sing you a lullaby!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.36,0:05:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.86,0:05:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But grownups don't need lullabies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.20,0:05:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Then can I sleep here with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.58,0:05:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.79,0:05:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But I thought you outgrew naps.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.54,0:05:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to take one today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.17,0:05:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly, Ann,\Nwould you go entertain our visitor?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.63,0:05:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate visitors.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.72,0:05:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,They all try to take you away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.85,0:05:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Ann.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.35,0:05:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But please, it's just for seven days.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.15,0:06:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Be a good girl for me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.78,0:06:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother said she'll be\Nresting for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.66,0:06:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.45,0:06:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,She's just a little sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.62,0:06:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll entertain you in the meantime.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.67,0:06:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate visitors,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.80,0:06:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,but you're a doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.14,0:06:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.18,0:06:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we could talk,\Nor play, or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.64,0:06:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That is outside my expertise.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.02,0:06:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.90,0:06:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,if it is only for a little while...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.03,0:06:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,-Then let's play with my doll!\N-Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.29,0:07:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,A doll playing with a doll,\Nthat's too funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.79,0:07:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What shall I do with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.67,0:07:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk to her, or take care of her,\Nobviously!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.22,0:07:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,First, you need to say hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.59,0:07:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.22,0:07:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.60,0:07:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.23,0:07:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The doll was the one who said that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.44,0:07:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.40,0:07:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.57,0:07:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right! You're a doll,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.66,0:07:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,so, you've never played\Nwith one of your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.08,0:07:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.08,0:07:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll teach you how!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.16,0:07:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Next, let's play house then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.62,0:07:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a table out in the yard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.67,0:07:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, your room is ready.\NI shall show you to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.25,0:07:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.92,0:07:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You will have to excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.64,0:07:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Your room is on the second floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.90,0:08:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what they're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.61,0:08:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ellis!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.20,0:08:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,-I'll go take that over!\N-Oh! You certainly may not!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.03,0:08:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.58,0:08:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't take it from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.79,0:08:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is life so unfair?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.37,0:09:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.29,0:09:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Ann.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.75,0:09:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Please come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.50,0:09:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.22,0:09:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.55,0:09:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I was adjusting my arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.51,0:09:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Adjusting?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.93,0:09:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, so it would move properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.35,0:09:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Then are you writing letters again\Ntomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.18,0:09:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yes.\N-And the next day?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.23,0:09:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yes.\N-Seven days, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.94,0:09:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,-The next day and the next?\N-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.07,0:09:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you writing it to?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.32,0:09:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That, I cannot say.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.66,0:09:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.12,0:09:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,-I have a duty to confidentiality.\N-Confi...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.16,0:09:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop using hard words!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.00,0:09:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.75,0:09:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.04,0:09:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Because my father's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.38,0:09:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You know that big war?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.84,0:09:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,He died a hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.51,0:10:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So, who are you writing this letter to?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.26,0:10:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Ann.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.02,0:10:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you come to see me for something?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.52,0:10:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.81,0:10:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ellis went home,\Nand mommy already went to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.32,0:10:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, Miss Ann,\Nyou should go to bed as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.16,0:10:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Why!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.70,0:10:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Staying up late is not good for a lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.54,0:10:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That is what Ms. Cattleya said.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.96,0:10:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.09,0:10:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Another Doll at my company.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.34,0:10:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,-Another one?\N-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.55,0:10:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,There are also other Dolls\Nnamed Miss Erica and Miss Iris.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.05,0:10:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! There's that many living dolls?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.56,0:10:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.27,0:10:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,-Miss Ann.\N-Fine! I'll go to bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.36,0:10:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better get to bed, too,\Nor my mommy will be mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.69,0:11:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you stay up too late,\Na ghost will come out to haunt you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.12,0:11:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night, Miss Ann.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.99,0:11:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.22,0:11:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What a weird doll!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.06,0:11:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,"The thief was surprised. He yelled, 'Ah!'
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.56,0:11:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And ran away."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.23,0:11:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You are quite good at reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.28,0:11:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.03,0:11:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of bread is really hard\Nand can't be eaten?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.45,0:11:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You could put it in soup to soften it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.46,0:11:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet! Violet!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.75,0:12:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Until my mom comes,\Nlet's do riddles and dance together
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.55,0:12:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and play house and catch bugs...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.22,0:12:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Ann.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.84,0:12:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Please tell me the order of priority.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.93,0:12:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet, read me a book.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.89,0:12:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.48,0:12:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.77,0:12:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What are your thoughts?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.78,0:12:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yes, it's very good.\N-Then I shall continue in this style.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.20,0:12:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.04,0:12:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,-Ann!\N-Oh, it's not what you think!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.71,0:12:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I was hoping Violet\Ncould tie a ribbon in my hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.38,0:12:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, but later, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.13,0:12:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Madam, would you allow me a short break?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.26,0:12:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.39,0:12:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe Miss Ann would like it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.48,0:12:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are, Miss Ann.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.48,0:13:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't want you to put\Nthe ribbon in my hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.90,0:13:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yes.\N-I really wanted my mommy to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.57,0:13:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yes.\N-And she's the one I want to read with...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.78,0:13:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,and do riddles and play house...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.95,0:13:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Although Mommy doesn't like bugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.50,0:13:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop taking away my time\Nwith my mommy, Violet!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.08,0:13:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only for a few more days.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.13,0:13:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Then tell my mommy I can be there\Nwhen you're writing your letter!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.09,0:13:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to be near her!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.93,0:13:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,All I want is to be close\Nand squeeze her hand. Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.56,0:13:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I am terribly sorry, I cannot do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.56,0:13:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.14,0:13:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Miss Ann.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.27,0:13:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I must be getting back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.57,0:13:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,-Do you think we could finish by today?\N-Yes, if we continue at this pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.91,0:13:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Madam, if you would.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.12,0:13:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Madam?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.58,0:14:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.09,0:14:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Madam!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.30,0:14:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,-I'm okay.\N-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.43,0:14:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.97,0:14:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,-Stop! That's enough! Mommy!\N-Miss Ann!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.97,0:14:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,-That's enough!\N-Ann.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.31,0:14:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm okay.\NSo, please go play in the other room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.02,0:14:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you writing this letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.28,0:14:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it for?\NDaddy isn't even with us anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.49,0:14:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,-It's an important letter.\N-It's for someone I don't know, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.00,0:14:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone who won't even come visit you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.66,0:14:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No one really cares about you anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.09,0:14:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the letter more important than me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.93,0:14:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing more important than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.68,0:15:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You're such a liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.48,0:15:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.44,0:15:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're not getting better at all!\NYou said you were going to get better!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.86,0:15:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.24,0:15:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I already know!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.95,0:15:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.78,0:15:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be all alone once you're gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.41,0:15:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,How much longer\Nwill I be able to be with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.30,0:15:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm going to be all alone anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.34,0:15:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,then stop writing some letter\Nand spend time with me now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.47,0:15:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.47,0:15:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.85,0:15:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,-Mommy!\N-Miss Ann.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.35,0:15:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.40,0:15:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Ann!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.22,0:16:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Ann.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.81,0:16:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to reassure you
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.39,0:16:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,that the time I am spending\Nwith your mother is for a good cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.65,0:16:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, I ask you not to be angry\Nwith your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.73,0:16:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.15,0:16:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.28,0:16:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It is only natural\Nthat this is painful for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.24,0:16:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You had to accept your mother's illness\Nat such a young age.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.49,0:16:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You are so strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.37,0:16:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.67,0:16:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.84,0:16:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.71,0:16:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I made my mommy cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.92,0:16:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.13,0:16:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You are a very kind person.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.51,0:16:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-I'm not.\N-You are.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.30,0:16:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.93,0:17:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not! I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.18,0:17:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,-My mommy got sick because I'm a bad girl!\N-Her illness is unrelated.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.48,0:17:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It is! It is!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.19,0:17:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,There is nothing...\NThere is nothing that can be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.28,0:17:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.61,0:17:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as my arms...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.16,0:17:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,can never be soft and warm like yours are.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.29,0:17:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,There is nothing that can be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.88,0:17:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Mommy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.18,0:17:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Mommy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.22,0:17:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is she writing a letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.89,0:17:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,People have feelings\Nthey want to express to others.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.44,0:17:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.15,0:17:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't need to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.99,0:18:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no such thing as a letter that\Ndoesn't deserve to be delivered, Miss Ann.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.34,0:18:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the day came\Nwhen the doll who embraced me
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.68,0:18:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,finished writing the letters\Nand it was time to say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.69,0:18:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.41,0:18:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,-Miss Ann.\N-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.25,0:18:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You're warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.34,0:18:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.34,0:19:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what about the tea you drank?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.93,0:19:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,As I said,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.18,0:19:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I will eventually expel it from my body\Nand it will return to the earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.40,0:19:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,She wasn't a doll after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.57,0:19:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And she wasn't bad news either.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.32,0:19:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,She was very kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.74,0:19:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I really wish I could have read\Nthe letters she wrote.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.54,0:19:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder who they were for.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.67,0:19:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ann.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.63,0:19:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's have some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.96,0:19:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's play with my doll, Mommy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.92,0:19:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,-Okay.\N-Then we can read books and play house...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.15,0:19:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ann.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.20,0:20:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ann.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.62,0:20:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,My Ann.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.73,0:20:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ann.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.94,0:20:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Ann.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.32,0:20:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy eighth birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.49,0:20:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,There might be many sad things happening,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.45,0:20:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and you might be feeling\Nreally overwhelmed right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.49,0:20:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't give up hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.08,0:20:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You might be sad and feel like crying,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.66,0:20:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,but don't forget:
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.12,0:20:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mother loves you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.30,0:21:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Ann, happy tenth birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.05,0:21:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you've grown quite a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.60,0:21:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm sure you still love reading\Nand dancing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.89,0:21:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you graduated from riddles and bugs?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.86,0:21:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy 18th birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.40,0:21:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a grown woman now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.82,0:21:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you in love?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.74,0:21:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't give you love advice,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.58,0:21:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'm sure whoever you choose\Nis a wonderful person.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.26,0:21:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy birthday, Ann.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.38,0:21:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You've lived for 20 years now.\NThat's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.05,0:21:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But remember that even adults\Nare allowed to complain sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.64,0:21:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Whenever you're feeling down,\Nremember that I am with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.69,0:22:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ann.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.94,0:22:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I will always,\Nalways be watching over you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.84,0:22:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Great work, Violet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.55,0:22:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You did so many!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.47,0:22:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,These letters are to be delivered\Nto Ann Magnolia for the next fifty years.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.44,0:22:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You wrote 50 letters?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.56,0:22:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It was your first long trip in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.27,0:22:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.94,0:22:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,-It was not a problem.\N-But this is so great.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.49,0:22:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,She's going to look forward\Nto these coming every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.32,0:22:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.45,0:22:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,by the time they arrive...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.71,0:22:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,her mother will...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.04,0:23:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,She's still so little.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.80,0:23:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,She gets so lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.38,0:23:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And Ann's mother has to leave\Nher precious daughter behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.97,0:23:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll be left all alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.51,0:23:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,in that mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.27,0:23:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.52,0:23:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.98,0:23:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to hold back my tears\Nthe whole time I was at the mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.03,0:23:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.78,0:23:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But, Violet...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.45,0:23:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,they will reach her.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.33,0:23:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The letters you wrote.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.96,0:23:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how far away she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.79,0:23:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,A LOVED ONE\NWILL ALWAYS WATCH OVER YOU
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.01,0:23:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Subtitle translation by\NZensho Yamamoto
